{"tid":916964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［on9 台仔］高雄民眾選後狂google「九二共識」 網友：搞不清楚就投了？","createTime":"2018-11-26T05:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T23:59:47.000Z","uid":20058,"like":249,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"99deff0fc6ca5b5fa4fd3ffb50268e10cbe06c63","tid":916964,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T05:22:49.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕九合一大選落幕，國民黨籍的高雄市長當選人韓國瑜表示認同九二共識，更說上任後會設立兩岸工作小組，有網友發現，「九二共識」一詞在Google的搜尋次數也瞬間飆升，並以高雄市居民搜尋量最多。<br />\n台中市長當選人盧秀燕被問到韓國瑜「九二共識拚經濟」的看法，則說九二共識是目前可以讓經濟好好發展的兩岸共識。根據「Google搜尋趨勢」資料顯示，在網路上搜尋「九二共識」一詞的民眾，在24日選舉結束後瞬間飆升，以縣市來分，高雄市居民搜尋量最多，其次是台中市、台北市、台南市、新北市。<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n不少網友得知此事後表示「九二共識是什麼都不知道就投了是不是」、「有點好笑，都搞不清楚就投了」、「先了解一下怎麼發財」、「無知真的很可怕」，也有網友說，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">這種現象與英國當初脫歐公投結束後，民眾才開始搜尋「什麼是歐盟」、「什麼是脫歐」的情形如出一轍。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ddcbb4f3d89ce1116ac28f26ff7e37a03a0f5777","tid":916964,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2624657\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2624657&d=ZCMZWLH%2B4d91uphMCSawODPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=615d8696\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2624657&h=55b6ee9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2624657</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880c8db4de462e88542c3cf25862b5668ba22724","tid":916964,"uid":123264,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"離島支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4051890c61bd0671d46d4e010f2249c934d06213","tid":916964,"uid":39796,"lik